</div>', '', '2026-03-21 07:05:33', '2026-03-21 07:05:33'),
(13, 'Course Success', 'Congratulations! You are officially enrolled ­¤Äō', '<div style=\'font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border-radius: 32px; background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #dcfce7; padding: 40px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\'>
