</div>', 'General', '2026-03-21 07:05:33', '2026-03-21 07:05:33'),
(14, 'Feedback Loop', 'How was your experience, [name]?', '<div style=\'font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 24px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\'>
